ncluding the Asymmetric Warfare Group, as well as the Navy’s elite SEAL Team 6.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511100616/http://www.marinecorpstimes.com/news/2007/02/atCarbine070219forafmcnt/|archivedate=2013年5月11日}}</ref>
